{"tid":1611372,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"真相有好多層次","createTime":"2019-10-02T02:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T02:52:06.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"813f5fe2e056ca87d9ee501f0c666d44f99ef2c4","tid":1611372,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:49:05.000Z","msg":"真相有好多層次<br />\n宇宙真相，人類也許永遠都不能知道。<br />\n我們連有冇外星人和外星生物都仲未知道。<br />\n科學真相，人類也可能極難研究成功。<br />\n人類的意識和靈魂之謎，謎底更難以解開。<br />\n<br />\n社會真相，以前係冇可能知道。<br />\n但人類進入無線互聯網年代，全球已經係connected，社會真相變成免費的公有產物，唯獨中國例外。中國因為有防水牆，所以知識水準仍停留在國際的1980年代。<br />\n<br />\n大家上上百度<br />\n搜索香港<br />\n清一色講香港人熱烈歡度慶祝國慶<br />\n對國殤示威活動隻字不提<br />\n更沒有警方開槍打示威者新聞<br />\n<br />\n中國人永遠得不到社會的真相<br />\n皆因國家防火牆城<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得世界網絡民主及自由法，是最重要的任務。要世人獲得社會真相，有尊嚴地活下去，首先要確保網絡自由。建議西方所有先進國家，限制網絡獨裁者官員及其家屬的出入境權利，凍結其海外資產，甚至學歷。"},{"pid":"47e0ad12ca0e702ecf24f1f5b5a6aa150b760aa3","tid":1611372,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:52:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.baidu.com/sf/vsearch?pd=realtime&amp;word=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&amp;tn=vsearch&amp;sa=vs_tab&amp;lid=8843403998088335489&amp;ms=1&amp;from=844b&amp;atn=index&amp;ivk_sa=1023197a&amp;rqid=8843403998088335489&amp;ssid=0&amp;from=844b&amp;uid=0&amp;pu=usm@10,sz@320_1001,ta@iphone_2_9.0_24_77.0&amp;bd_page_type=1&amp;baiduid=00BEB0EB492147B819D91713BD0D022D&amp;tj=realtime_1_0_10_l2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.baidu.com%2Fsf%2Fvsearch%3Fpd%3Drealtime%26word%3D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%26tn%3Dvsearch%26sa%3Dvs_tab%26lid%3D8843403998088335489%26ms%3D1%26from%3D844b%26atn%3Dindex%26ivk_sa%3D1023197a%26rqid%3D8843403998088335489%26ssid%3D0%26from%3D844b%26uid%3D0%26pu%3Dusm%4010%2Csz%40320_1001%2Cta%40iphone_2_9.0_24_77.0%26bd_page_type%3D1%26baiduid%3D00BEB0EB492147B819D91713BD0D022D%26tj%3Drealtime_1_0_10_l2&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=b8bd2f67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.baidu.com/sf/vsearch?pd=realtime&amp;word=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&amp;tn=vsearch&amp;sa=vs_tab&amp;lid=8843403998088335489&amp;ms=1&amp;from=844b&amp;atn=index&amp;ivk_sa=1023197a&amp;rqid=8843403998088335489&amp;ssid=0&amp;from=844b&amp;uid=0&amp;pu=usm@10,sz@320_1001,ta@iphone_2_9.0_24_77.0&amp;bd_page_type=1&amp;baiduid=00BEB0EB492147B819D91713BD0D022D&amp;tj=realtime_1_0_10_l2</a>"}]}